@startuml complete_workflow_sequence
!theme plain
title Complete System Workflow - Patient Registration to X-ray Analysis

actor Reception as rec
actor "General Doctor" as gd
actor "Specialist Doctor" as sd
actor "X-ray Technician" as tech
actor Admin as admin
participant "System" as sys
participant "Database" as db
participant "AI Model" as ai
participant "Notification" as notif

== Patient Registration ==
rec -> sys: Register Patient
sys -> sys: Generate Patient ID (PAT####)
sys -> db: Store Patient Data
db -> sys: Confirm Registration
sys -> notif: Notify General Doctors
sys -> rec: Registration Successful

== Patient Triage ==
notif -> gd: New Patient Registered
gd -> sys: View Registered Patients
sys -> db: Query Registered Patients
db -> sys: Return Patient List
sys -> gd: Display Patients

gd -> sys: Refer Patient to Specialist
sys -> db: Update Patient Status to 'referred'
sys -> db: Set referred_to field
db -> sys: Confirm Referral
sys -> notif: Notify Specialist Doctor
sys -> gd: Referral Success

== X-ray Request Creation ==
notif -> sd: Patient Referred to You
sd -> sys: View Referred Patients
sys -> db: Query Referred Patients
db -> sys: Return Patient List
sys -> sd: Display Referred Patients

sd -> sys: Create X-ray Request
sys -> db: Create X-ray Request Record
sys -> db: Update Patient Status to 'xray_requested'
db -> sys: Confirm Request Creation
sys -> notif: Notify X-ray Technicians
sys -> sd: Request Created

== X-ray Processing ==
notif -> tech: New X-ray Request
tech -> sys: View Pending Requests
sys -> db: Query Pending Requests
db -> sys: Return Request Queue
sys -> tech: Display Requests

tech -> sys: Upload X-ray Image (JPEG/PNG)
sys -> ai: Analyze for Cardiomegaly
ai -> sys: Return Prediction & Confidence
sys -> db: Store Results
sys -> db: Update Request Status to 'completed'
db -> sys: Confirm Storage
sys -> notif: Notify Requesting Doctor
sys -> tech: Analysis Complete

== Results Review ==
notif -> sd: X-ray Result Ready
sd -> sys: View X-ray Results
sys -> db: Query Prediction Results
db -> sys: Return AI Analysis
sys -> sd: Display Results (Positive/Negative + Confidence)

== Administrative Oversight ==
admin -> sys: Monitor System Overview
sys -> db: Query System Metrics
db -> sys: Return Analytics
sys -> admin: Display Dashboard with Charts

admin -> sys: View Diagnosis Data
sys -> db: Query All Predictions
db -> sys: Return Diagnosis Records
sys -> admin: Display Filterable Data

== Patient Data Edit (Optional) ==
rec -> sys: Request Patient Edit
sys -> db: Create Edit Request
db -> sys: Confirm Request
sys -> admin: Notify Edit Request

admin -> sys: Review Edit Request
admin -> sys: Approve Request
sys -> db: Update Request Status
sys -> notif: Notify Reception
sys -> admin: Approval Confirmed

rec -> sys: Submit Patient Changes
sys -> db: Store Proposed Changes
sys -> admin: Notify Final Approval Needed

admin -> sys: Final Approval
sys -> db: Apply Changes to Patient Record
sys -> db: Update Request Status to 'approved_final'
db -> sys: Confirm Updates
sys -> admin: Changes Applied Successfully

@enduml